cap-alert (1.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add replay_hours (default 4) to throttle tail replays of unchanged NWS
    alerts; new or changed alerts still play immediately.
  * Fix scheduled timer runs clearing the replay hold every poll cycle.
  * Document Piper/asl-tts voice selection and alert replay interval in README.

 -- Jory A. Pratt <geekypenguin@gmail.com>  Sun, 28 Jun 2026 16:50:00 -0500

cap-alert (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release as cap-alert (renamed from cap-warn).
  * Replaces cap-warn with automatic migration of config, state, logs, and timer.
  * Same feature set: NWS alerts, geo hazards, GPS, quiet hours, Pushover, and
    asterisk-user runtime with hardened permissions.

 -- Jory A. Pratt <geekypenguin@gmail.com>  Sun, 28 Jun 2026 12:00:00 -0500
